injuries.longComment: There was no injury reported, so Tyson may have just been given the night off for the Nuggets to get a look at other players. It remains to be seen if Tyson will suit up Friday against the Lakers.
injuries.shortComment: Tyson (undisclosed) did not play in Thursday's Summer League game against the Clippers.
